4)title: Choice Specs Dragapult + Power Herb Heatran Bulky Offense by beatiful
5)notes: This is a team that I made to use in SPL. It is bulky offense with Choice Specs Dragapult and Power Herb + Solar Beam Heatran/comma/ two broken Pokemon that I wanted to use. The team is based on playing aggressive with the help of the momentum that Teleport Slowking and U-turn Landorus-T give. I wanted to give Bisharp Assault Vest because Dragapult is a big problem for the team/comma/ and even without Sword Dance/comma/ Bisharp is still a good breaker with Future Sight + Teleport Slowking. Rillaboom was the last Pokemon on the team; I thought about it because it helps Heatran's Solar Beam a lot with its Grassy Surge ability/comma/ and it has Grassy Glide/comma/ a priority attack that hits quite hard and also helps to revenge kill faster Pokemon. This team is fun and easy to play with/comma/ and I hope you all enjoy it.
